qas.question: What is lite AC otherwise known as?
What is Christian AC a subgenre of?
Along with hot, soft, urban and Christian AC, what is another prominent time of adult contemporary music?

context: Over the years, AC has spawned subgenres including "hot AC", "<a0_0>soft AC<a0_0/>" (also known as "lite AC"), "urban AC", "<a2_0>rhythmic AC<a2_0/>", and "Christian AC" (a softer type of <a1_0>contemporary Christian music<a1_0/>). Some stations play only "hot AC", "soft AC", or only one of the variety of subgenres. Therefore, it is not usually considered a specific genre of music; it is merely an assemblage of selected tracks from musicians of many different genres.
